I"j<p>Lawnmower has gone 10 years without a service.</p>

<!-- more -->
<p>The mower is a Honda HRU19D, the closest manual I coukd find is
the one for the <a href="/assets/images/2020/04/hru19k1.pdf">HRU19K1</a>.
While there are lots of good videos (such as
<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s2NcBVRMvKs">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s2NcBVRMvKs</a>), for those of us
that prefer to read, here are step by step instructions. I estimate
that having this done outside would be about $200.</p>

<p>This mower has run flawlessly for 10 years but in the past year
has become hard to start. Needs a carburettor clean and while Iâ€™m at
it, might as well service everything.</p>

