<h2 id="step-1">Step 1</h2>
<p>Shut off the fuel tap on the hose that runs into the carby.
Take off the air filter cover and the 2 10mm bolts that go into the
engine.</p>

<figure class="">
  <a href="/assets/images/2020/04/mower2.jpeg">
  <img src="/assets/images/2020/04/mower2.jpeg" alt="" />
  
